        "title": "build(deps): bump the swift-deps group across 1 directory with 2 updates",
        "body": "Bumps the swift-deps group with 2 updates in the /apps/macos directory: [github.com/steipete/peekaboo](https://github.com/steipete/Peekaboo) and [github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras](https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras).\n\nUpdates `github.com/steipete/peekaboo` from 3.5.2 to 3.5.3\n<details>\n<summary>Commits</summary>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/f22e46cc1aedf2c409e2fbb07efe6c9577662f38\"><code>f22e46c</code></a> chore(release): prepare 3.5.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/4f2b0e9cb4ac702086bcbcec7fe3eb4d24793287\"><code>4f2b0e9</code></a> fix: harden background computer automation</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/5fba9b79de8952bced8f3160b8a47f1e8e2f13b1\"><code>5fba9b7</code></a> docs: refresh project banner (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/steipete/Peekaboo/issues/190\">#190</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/3aaa96bfa49f2bc4afbe3f7f6aace7e3a2af32b1\"><code>3aaa96b</code></a> fix: filter background apps from app list (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/steipete/Peekaboo/issues/189\">#189</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/8cf0796692683dd501cd858f31997405fa746594\"><code>8cf0796</code></a> Fix clicks on hidden menu extras (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/steipete/Peekaboo/issues/188\">#188</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/26c729129279a647d507ec6b0eb5cb6bb427c0c4\"><code>26c7291</code></a> docs(changelog): open 3.5.3</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/openclaw/Peekaboo/commit/84100e4cc154126c2dd45541bd499fbe6a4609ea\"><code>84100e4</code></a> chore(release): update appcast for 3.5.2</li>\n<li>See full diff in <a href=\"https://github.com/steipete/Peekaboo/compare/v3.5.2...v3.5.3\">compare view</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<br />\n\nUpdates `github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras` from 1.3.2 to 1.4.0\n<details>\n<summary>Release notes</summary>\n<p><em>Sourced from <a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/releases\">github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras's releases</a>.</em></p>\n<blockquote>\n<h2>1.4.0</h2>\n<h2>What's Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Added: A new <code>ConcurrencyExtrasTestSupport</code> module with <code>TaskLocalTrait</code> (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/65\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#65</a>).</li>\n<li>Fixed: <code>Result.init(catching:)</code> is now <code>nonisolated(nonsending)</code> (thanks <a href=\"https://github.com/rhysm94\"><code>@​rhysm94</code></a>, <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/61\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#61</a>).</li>\n<li>Fixed: Enable <code>NonisolatedNonsendingByDefault</code> (thanks <a href=\"https://github.com/davdroman\"><code>@​davdroman</code></a>, <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/64\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#64</a>).</li>\n<li>Infrastructure: Simplify Android CI (thanks <a href=\"https://github.com/marcprux\"><code>@​marcprux</code></a>, <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/53\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#53</a>).</li>\n<li>Infrastructure: Bump package versioning requirements (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/58\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#58</a>).</li>\n<li>Infrastructure: Update format.yml (thanks <a href=\"https://github.com/rhysm94\"><code>@​rhysm94</code></a>, <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/62\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#62</a>).</li>\n<li>Infrastructure: Bump CI (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/63\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#63</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>New Contributors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/marcprux\"><code>@​marcprux</code></a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/53\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#53</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rhysm94\"><code>@​rhysm94</code></a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/61\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#61</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/davdroman\"><code>@​davdroman</code></a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/pull/64\">pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras#64</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/compare/1.3.2...1.4.0\">https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/compare/1.3.2...1.4.0</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>Commits</summary>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/a90e2e40a7a840a853dd29e57cbef5dbb72c9d5b\"><code>a90e2e4</code></a> Add <code>ConcurrencyExtrasTestSupport</code> with <code>TaskLocalTrait</code> (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/issues/65\">#65</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/5766c2e1f581fc9702a881ec3ff08371d88e637c\"><code>5766c2e</code></a> Cleanup</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/5d81c23fdb9715201c4015a1973ea7ab6bc06b37\"><code>5d81c23</code></a> Enable <code>NonisolatedNonsendingByDefault</code> (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/issues/64\">#64</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/f9db8422fa13f554987eba71887f9652c4a46b9b\"><code>f9db842</code></a> Remove documentation workflow</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/f7b9b8c62ed2533bf8ad1665ccd9e7a682c54d8f\"><code>f7b9b8c</code></a> Bump CI (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/issues/63\">#63</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/e516f471ebfac46b04c22af03dcfcc25f48af760\"><code>e516f47</code></a> Run swift-format</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/cb9c6e00c5c9691d905c4c460913e82ee45ac39e\"><code>cb9c6e0</code></a> Update format.yml (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/issues/62\">#62</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/45bfc4e93340888206b247005a8224ab2e10b6e9\"><code>45bfc4e</code></a> Run swift-format</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/5fe9f3bdc0ade508cfbee611119ec87cc1c414f2\"><code>5fe9f3b</code></a> <code>nonisolated(nonsending)</code> Result <code>init</code> (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/issues/61\">#61</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/commit/d74eaaa106e66184655982433b10a2f2dffbe2ac\"><code>d74eaaa</code></a> Update package versioning (<a href=\"https://redirect.github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/issues/58\">#58</a>)</li>\n<li>Additional commits viewable in <a href=\"https://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-concurrency-extras/compare/1.3.2...1.4.0\">compare view</a></li>\n</ul>\n</details>\n<br />\n",
